<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="../assets/xml/rss.xsl" media="all"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>paregorios.org (Posts about hackday)</title><link>http://paregorios.org/</link><description></description><atom:link href="http://paregorios.org/categories/hackday.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><language>en</language><copyright>Contents Â© 2018 &lt;a href="mailto:paregorios@hotmail.com"&gt;Tom Elliott&lt;/a&gt; </copyright><lastBuildDate>Fri, 06 Apr 2018 22:06:17 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>Nikola (getnikola.com)</generator><docs>http://blogs.law.harvard.edu/tech/rss</docs><item><title>Pleiades Hackday: Improving Descriptions</title><link>http://paregorios.org/posts/2012/12/pleiades-hackday-improving-descriptions/</link><dc:creator>Tom Elliott</dc:creator><description>&lt;span style="font-family: inherit;"&gt;A Pleiades hack day is now underway in the &lt;a href="http://pleiades.stoa.org/help/content/pleiades-irc"&gt;Pleiades IRC channel&lt;/a&gt;. We've decided to focus on cleaning up descriptions for Pleiades place resources on the island of Sardinia. The following query gives you most of the Pleiades content for Sardinia and Corsica:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: inherit;"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: inherit;"&gt;&lt;span style="background-color: white;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://tinyurl.com/aotxaum"&gt;http://tinyurl.com/aotxaum&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b style="background-color: white;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: inherit;"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: inherit;"&gt;Here's our process:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: inherit;"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;Pick a place to improve&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Drop the title and URL into the IRC channel, so everyone knows you're working on it&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Check out a working copy of the place&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;In your working copy, write a better description and connect the place to the place resource for the island you're working on.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Submit for review&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Ping paregorios or servilius_ahala in IRC to get it reviewed and published&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;We're also building an FAQ on the subject of "&lt;a href="https://docs.google.com/a/nyu.edu/document/d/1GGBk3ROB_TVq1u02qKTFNXza_YoJYYhxIutVXCPeg38/edit"&gt;What Makes a Good Pleiades Description?&lt;/a&gt;".&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana, Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: x-small;"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;</description><category>hackday</category><category>pleiades</category><guid>http://paregorios.org/posts/2012/12/pleiades-hackday-improving-descriptions/</guid><pubDate>Thu, 06 Dec 2012 23:23:00 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>